The onboarding `PulsePresetsStep` currently calls `PresetCard` with `enabled` and `onToggle` props (the old API). After this shim, `PulsePresetsStep` will typecheck against the new `PresetCardProps` interface which uses `variant`, `checked`, and `onCheckedChange`. **This will cause a TypeScript error in `PulsePresetsStep`** — that breakage is intentional and is fixed in task 1.3.

